Instructions to set up the application for the first time
---------------------------------------------------------

1. Ensure you have Ruby and MySQL installed.

2. Install the right version of rails:

gem install -v=2.3.4 rails

3. Install god

gem install god

4. Run set up scripts:

rake gems:install
rake db:create
rake db:migrate

5. Run everything

god ./config/nuntium.god

6. Point your browser to localhost:3000
